data.description: POOL HOME!!  Darling 3 bed, 2 bath home in Fort Mohave.  Home features large open living room with vaulted ceilings.  Kitchen with trendy backsplash, lots of cabinets and counter space.  New garbage disposal.  Gas stove/oven.  Both casual and formal dining areas.  Large master suite with walk in closet.  Master bathroom has been remodeled with new vanity, walk in shower.  All new plumbing.  Two good sized guest bedrooms (one has free standing closet that will stay) and full guest bath with tub shower combo.  Extra long covered car port and side parking for toys.  Back yard  has in ground fiberglass pool and cute cabana area. Tiled roof.  Man cave workshop, too!  Just a stones throw from the Colorado River, Lake Mohave, shopping, dining, medical, and schools.  Some furnishings can stay.  Buyer to verify all pertinent info including sq footage, flood zones, utility, etc.
